<body><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">7天，磨砺耳朵的英语语感；同时拓展词汇量，复习语法。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 18px;">雷哥单词</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">重磅推出</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体;">听力训练营</span></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);"><strong style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">7天<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Calibri;">360</span>°无死角的提升听力，还有<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Calibri;">1600</span>元大奖拿活动</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">活动内容：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">每天一篇精选好文，一文四听</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: 宋体;">一、</span><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: 宋体;">听：空耳听</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">二、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">二听，对照原文，尝试听取关键词；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">三、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">听老师讲解核心词汇，语法及相关风俗文化</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">四、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">提交阅读理解题答案，完成打卡</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">活动奖励：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">第一名：听力、写作、方法课等任选</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">11</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">节课（线下课程一节课价值</span><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: Calibri;">500</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">元）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">第二名：课程代金券</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">500元（代金券有效期3个月）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">第三名：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">1W雷豆（价值100元）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">活动时间：</span></strong><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);">11月<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;">15</span>日<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;">-12</span>月<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;">21</span>日</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;"><br/></span>报名请扫描下方二维码</p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/files/attach/images/20181108/1541645202177494.jpg" title="1541645202177494.jpg" alt="“雷哥英语说”公众平台.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p>
